author: Michael Roberts
title: The Twelve Halloween Costumes Googled Most in Colorado
text:
Additional images below. HalloweenCostumes.com Estately, the website that revealed the top ten cities for douchebags (including two in Colorado ) is back with a timely list : "The Costume Ideas Each State Googles More Than Any Other State."
Findings are based on a whopping eleven years of Google Trends data.
The results are both fun and practical — since by steering clear of the most Googled Colorado concepts, you can decrease the chances that you'll show up at a party wearing the same outfit as three other people.
Here are the twelve costumes that were searched most frequently by Coloradans, followed by an Estately graphic showing favorites from every state. To see the original post, with much more information, click here .
